@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hkvfio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.18 + v0 + 0.38)) * ((v1 + 0.01 - v0 + 0.90) * (v0 + 0.01 * v2 + 0.28)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.62 - tmp + 0.24)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.12) * v0))
    v2 = v0
    tmp = 0.05
    data[tid] = v0
